Title: Remote Voting
Description:
Postgraduate work. The main aim is to create remote voting system addapted for Russian Federation. 
Some interesting staff regarding ICAO e-passport reading and image parsing. 
It's developed in C#. Main technologies: WCF, WPF, EF 4.1, Unity, Smart Card protocols.
